Insider Activity


Individual




John W. Diercksen



Mr. John W. Diercksen is a Principal at Greycrest LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Popular, Inc., Intelsat SA and Intelsat Corp. Mr. Diercksen was previously employed as an Independent Director by Harman International Industries, Inc., Executive VP-Strategy, Development & Planning by Verizon Communications, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Bell Atlantic Directory Group, Treasurer & Vice President-Finance by NYNEX Corp., a Principal by Insurance Co. of North America (UK) Ltd., a Principal by American Can Co., a Principal by Coleco Industries, Inc., Chief Financial & Information Officer by Directory Group, Director-International Costs & Budgets by International Playtex, Inc., and a Principal by Lever Brothers Co. He also served on the board at Verizon Telematics, Inc., Terremark Worldwide, Inc., SuperMedia, Inc., Idearc, Inc. and New Communications Holdings, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Iona College and an MBA from Pace University.



